    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Cursed Ones</strong> is a 1-2 player co-op horror stealth survival game. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play as the Crane siblings as you continue your late parents' legacy to purge the world of sinister spirits.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Track down the items used to summon the spirit by any means necessary. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong><i>Make sure you both don't die in the process.</i></strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3135050/extras/8d0b3b2f08b00a09294e11fe454160db.webp?t=1729877665\" width=350 height=38 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3135050/extras/9250b4fbefdd7fe8c02c1e12212bf3fe.poster.avif?t=1729877665\" width=600 height=234 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3135050/extras/9250b4fbefdd7fe8c02c1e12212bf3fe.webm?t=1729877665\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3135050/extras/9250b4fbefdd7fe8c02c1e12212bf3fe.mp4?t=1729877665\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Protect each other</strong>: Play with a friend as you <strong>HIDE</strong>, <strong>RUN</strong>, or <strong>CONFRONT</strong> the spirit that is hunting you down.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Singleplayer Mode</strong>: Ditch your sibling and take on the supernatural yourself.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Scavenge the map</strong>: Find items around the map that will help you survive.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3135050/extras/504abb02356a30532ed857b4d04f0835.webp?t=1729877665\" width=211 height=40 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3135050/extras/bdce0054558121f77a923ef851c03e5e.poster.avif?t=1729877665\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3135050/extras/bdce0054558121f77a923ef851c03e5e.webm?t=1729877665\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3135050/extras/bdce0054558121f77a923ef851c03e5e.mp4?t=1729877665\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Find out what happened</strong>: There are clues around the world that hint at how tragedy struck those who were there before you.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Equipment</strong>: As ghost hunters, you always carry the right equipment for the job. Each map will have unique equipment for that particular map.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The Crane Curse</strong>: Cursed blood runs through the Crane family line, and each sibling has a special curse. Find out what it is.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Getting Caught</strong>: If you're caught there are no second chances. Make sure to protect each other. </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3135050/extras/2889efe01235dc17cffe3207d9e09cd8.webp?t=1729877665\" width=326 height=38 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3135050/extras/205f393df936828b6932152ed2246941.poster.avif?t=1729877665\" width=600 height=254 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3135050/extras/205f393df936828b6932152ed2246941.webm?t=1729877665\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3135050/extras/205f393df936828b6932152ed2246941.mp4?t=1729877665\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The Goal</strong>: Track down and destroy the items that were used to bring the spirit into our world &amp; <strong>MAKE IT OUT ALIVE</strong></p></li></ul>",
